rong** — 5 wasted sessions today on the same state corruption bug\n6. **Lessons learned** — ralph reconciliation needs proof-document-aware logic\n7. **Action items** — fix the reconciliation bug\n\nWrite the retrospective to _bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/session-retro-2026-03-27.md. Since a retro for today already exists, append to it with a `---` separator and timestamp.\n\nDo NOT ask the user any questions — proceed autonomously.\nDo NOT run git commit. Do NOT run git add. Do NOT modify sprint-status.yaml.","subagent_type":"general-purpose"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":111,"cache_read_input_tokens":57408,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":111},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"3dac35af-df1a-4f37-9c9f-763ee24e5ad0","uuid":"483a9ac3-45da-4f98-abb8-a221890f1bf2"}
